Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class PlayerMove

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.PlayerMove
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PlayerMoveEnd
public class PlayerMove
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
PlayerMove class is sent to server by client to show his move. It contains all the information about player's move: Player who is making move, Worker of the player, two integers row and column indicating the cell in which the player wants his worker to move or build.
